description:
The purpose of this compilation is to improve the overall graphical quality of the game as well as to save the user from a hassle of searching for patches/texturepacks/plugins and whatnot. Can also be used as a platform for further plugin extension.

Contains :

- Morrowind, Tribunal, Bloodmoon (1.6.1820);
- All official Bethesda plugins;
- MGEXE 0.9.10 (Hrnchamd);
- Morrowind Code Patch (Hrnchamd, Psyringe);
- Morrowind Visual Pack 1024 (Ayse, Lord Gabryael, Qarl, Raptre, &amp; Zuldazug);
- Darknut's Morrowind Armor Textures
- Darknut's Creature Textures (Darknut);
- Darknut's Creature Textures Tribunal (Darknut);
- Darknut's Creature Textures Bloodmoon (Darknut);
- Darknut's Creature Textures addendum (Darknut);
- Darknut's Dwemer Ruin Textures (Darknut);
- Darknut's Little Weapons Mod Complete (Darknut);
- Bloom Enhanced Lighting (Nelothsmouth);
- Morrowind Grass Mod (Vality, Yacoby, Liztail);
- Kirel's Interior Weather (Kirel)
- Leafy Trees (Irmekroache);
- Mesh Improvements (Armed_Defender);
- Skies .IV (starwarsgal9875);
- Unofficial Morrowind Patch 1.6.5 (BTB);
- Better Heads 2.0 (Gorg &amp; Arathrax, Motoki);
- Better Bodies 2.2 (Psychodog Studios);
- Better Clothes (Psychodog Studios);

Screenshots: http://imgur.com/a/odPVn

Installation :
- Unpack;
- Run MGEgui.exe to setup the screen resolution;
- Run Morrowind.exe
